item.title: How to Study [Book]
item.description: How to Study. Swain, George Fillmore. Jan 1, 1917. Dad got us a kindle when I was in high school. This book was on it, and so I read all of it. I don’t think I’d have stumbled on it in the wild. Given that it was written in 1917, it should be interesting to see what still holds.
